licted Obamacare on us, while exempting all members of Congress from it.\n- Don't let folks forget: (D)ems funded mentally ill cross-dressers visiting schools.\n\nThe electorate, as a whole, has the collective memory of a used sweatsock. (Don't blame me, that's the clay we have to work with.)  So please, don't let your constituents forget.\n\n[dc_draino](https://x.com/dc_draino/status/2022833645531103378)", "author": "greatpumpkin", "created": 1771180000768, "profile_picture": "THJfFaQLwuCH", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "To all political candidates - remind the electorate of what your opponent truly stands for, by running advertisements with their own words. Do not let the public forget.", "last_comment_created": 1771180000768, "content": "<p>Politicians love sound-bites.  So dig back, and <em><strong>use those very same words against them in your advertisments.</strong></em>  Remind folks just who each individual (D) is.</p>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: they wanted open borders.</li>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: they voted against voter ID.</li>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: they voted for annualized 9.5% O'Biden-flation.</li>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: they wanted grandma dying alone in a senior home.</li>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: they celebrated Charlie Kirk's death, after burning down city centers for George Floyd.</li>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: (D)ems inflicted Obamacare on us, while exempting all members of Congress from it.</li>\n<li>Don't let folks forget: (D)ems funded mentally ill cross-dressers visiting schools.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The electorate, as a whole, has the collective memory of a used sweatsock. (Don't blame me, that's the clay we have to work with.)  So please, don't let your constituents forget.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://x.com/dc_draino/status/2022833645531103378\" target=\"_blank\">dc_draino</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 19, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}], "status": true}